data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this beautiful, lovingly cared-for 4 Bedroom home with North/South orientation on oversized lot in Tartesso! Light & bright,flowing floor plan has 9' ceilings, large 20x20 tile & spacious Great Room that opens to patio. Kitchen boasts 36'' upper cabinets, single-basin sink, gas stove, eased edge Bengal White 3cm granite tops. Relax in style in the large Primary Suite. Plenty of room for office & guests, including a split bedroom at front for privacy. Smart Home, includes programmable thermostat & quiet Liftmaster wireless garage door opener & much more. Large yard offers so many pool or landscape possibilities. Tartesso amenities abound: paths, parks, splashpad, sports park with ball & soccer, basketball & volleyball. Tour it today before it's gone!
